{"tid":92369,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[繼續倒數]傳聞香港o既中資行幫手查中國客走資","createTime":"2017-01-23T14:03:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T11:12:38.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9d6144f4852091141661dfae769dc109d1feb64c","tid":92369,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:03:50.000Z","msg":"<strong>【暴力打走資】<br />\n錢落到香港都查！傳港中資行查中國客轉賬</strong><br />\n\t<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0123 10:16<br />\n<br />\n中國嚴打走資，除了在今年初開始，嚴格執行中國居民購滙須詳細申報用途之外，《信報》消息指出，有個別本港中資銀行疑配合總行做法，<strong>包括遇上中國客戶透過<span style=\"color: red;\">本港賬戶</span>進行第三方支付時，罕有地<span style=\"color: red;\">詳問其用途</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n報導指，其中一個個案，是早前已在本港利用保費融資（Premium Financing）投保的私人銀行中國客戶，擬從中資銀行轉賬至私人銀行以繳付保險供款利息，惟超過兩星期仍未完成，情況罕見。消息透露，部份過去積極轉介高檔客戶往香港分支私人銀行的中國銀行，近期暫停跨境客戶轉介，避免不慎牴觸中國嚴防資金外流的措施。<br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170123/56210268\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170123%2F56210268&d=c3cgBaPJNXi1TLONh%2BUXR4scwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=8218e3e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170123%2F56210268&h=df3875e7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170123/56210268</a>"},{"pid":"be8bc1f3b5796f8de2d68219899c1a1dd3e86326","tid":92369,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:56:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11eec9a62c4a969de87c575cd7f20cd8629f026","tid":92369,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T10:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41f438b0c9a64b803ba094be35f55bc3b5060e7","tid":92369,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T11:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" 